WEBVTT

00:11:57.976 --> 00:12:00.487
and you're thinking about
what you're going to wear,

00:12:00.511 --> 00:12:03.327
I hope you appreciate the process

00:12:03.351 --> 00:12:05.777
and think about how what you chose

00:12:06.330 --> 00:12:07.970
makes you feel.

00:12:07.994 --> 00:12:10.572
Today, Oliver is 13.

00:12:10.596 --> 00:12:12.765
He wears his adaptive khakis,

00:12:12.789 --> 00:12:15.014
his magnetic button-front shirt --

00:12:15.038 --> 00:12:16.770
feels like the coolest kid around.

00:12:17.370 --> 00:12:19.952
My boy has total swagger.

00:12:20.282 --> 00:12:21.432
(Laughter)

00:12:23.966 --> 00:12:25.329
As I mentioned,

00:12:27.557 --> 00:12:29.800
Oliver's disease is degenerative,